<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>危險性化學物質緊急應變規劃 (Hazardous Chemical ERP Infographic)</title>
  
  <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  
  <!-- Lucide Icons -->
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }
    
    /* Custom Scrollbar for the Navigation */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 8px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: #1e293b;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: #eab308; 
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
      background: #ca8a04; 
    }

    .section-transition {
      transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    /* Animation Utilities */
    @keyframes pulse-slow {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
      50% { opacity: 0.5; }
    }
    .animate-pulse-slow {
      animation: pulse-slow 3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-100 text-slate-800 antialiased overflow-x-hidden">

  <!-- ================= Navigation ================= -->
  <nav id="sidebar" class="fixed top-0 right-0 h-full bg-slate-900 text-white w-64 transform translate-x-full md:translate-x-0 md:w-20 md:hover:w-64 transition-all duration-300 z-50 shadow-2xl group flex flex-col">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 md:hidden">
      <span class="font-bold text-lg text-yellow-500">目錄</span>
      <button onclick="toggleMenu()" class="p-2"><i data-lucide="x"></i></button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto py-4 space-y-1">
      <!-- Nav Items generated by JS -->
      <div id="nav-items-container"></div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Mobile Menu Button -->
  <button onclick="toggleMenu()" class="fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 bg-slate-800 text-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-lg md:hidden hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors">
    <i data-lucide="menu"></i>
  </button>

  <!-- ================= Main Content ================= -->
  <main class="md:pr-20 transition-all duration-300">

    <!-- PAGE 1: Cover -->
    <section id="section-0" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-slate-800 text-white relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl w-full text-center space-y-12 z-10">
        <div class="inline-block p-6 rounded-full bg-yellow-500 bg-opacity-20 mb-8 animate-pulse-slow">
          <i data-lucide="shield" class="w-20 h-20 text-yellow-500"></i>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tight leading-tight">
            危險性化學物質<br/>緊急應變規劃
          </h1>
          <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-yellow-400 font-light">
            從「法規合規」邁向「組織韌性」
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-16 text-left">
          <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border-t-4 border-blue-500 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <i data-lucide="shield" class="mr-2 text-blue-400"></i>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">預防 (Prevention)</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">避免事故發生的本質安全設計與管理。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border-t-4 border-yellow-500 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <i data-lucide="list" class="mr-2 text-yellow-400"></i>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">整備 (Preparedness)</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">事故發生前的資源盤點、計畫撰寫與實兵演練。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm border-t-4 border-red-500 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-center mb-3">
              <i data-lucide="flame" class="mr-2 text-red-400"></i>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-2xl">應變 (Response)</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-300">事故發生後的黃金時間損害控管與救災。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-lg text-slate-400 text-base">
          講師：何明信 (職安衛技師、退休檢查員、創贊公司、成大環醫所) | 2025年12月
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Background Abstract Elements -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-10 left-10 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-10 w-64 h-64 bg-purple-500 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PAGE 2: Golden Triangle -->
    <section id="section-1" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl w-full">
        <!-- Section Title Component -->
        <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
          <div class="text-yellow-600 font-bold text-base tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">PAGE 2</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-2">安全管理的黃金三角</h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium">三者缺一不可的動態循環</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative mt-12 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 w-full relative z-10">
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div class="order-1 flex flex-col items-center text-center group cursor-default">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-blue-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-4 border-blue-500 group-hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i data-lucide="search" class="w-10 h-10 text-blue-600"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">風險評估<br/>(Risk Assessment)</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-blue-100">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-700">起點</span><br/>
                必須辨識出「最壞情境」(Worst Case)，否則應變計畫形同虛設。
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div class="order-2 md:order-3 flex flex-col items-center text-center group cursor-default">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-4 border-red-500 group-hover:bg-red-200 transition-colors shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i data-lucide="activity" class="w-10 h-10 text-red-600"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">緊急應變<br/>(Emergency Response)</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-red-100">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700">對策</span><br/>
                不是紙上作業，而是面對殘餘風險的最後一道防線。
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div class="order-3 md:order-2 flex flex-col items-center text-center group cursor-default">
              <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-4 border-4 border-green-500 group-hover:bg-green-200 transition-colors shadow-lg group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                <i data-lucide="check-square" class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600"></i>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">事故調查<br/>(Incident Investigation)</h3>
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm group-hover:shadow-md transition-shadow border border-green-100">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">修正</span><br/>
                調查結果必須回饋修正「風險評估的假設」與「應變計畫」。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Connecting Arrows (SVG for better responsiveness) -->
          <svg class="hidden md:block absolute top-12 left-0 w-full h-full pointer-events-none -z-0" viewBox="0 0 800 200" preserveAspectRatio="none">
            <path d="M 150 60 L 400 150 L 650 60" fill="none" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="8,8" />
            <path d="M 150 60 Q 400 -20 650 60" fill="none" stroke="#cbd5e1" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="8,8" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PAGE 3: Compliance -->
    <section id="section-2" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-5xl w-full">
        <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
          <div class="text-yellow-600 font-bold text-base tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">PAGE 3</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-2">台灣法規硬指標</h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium">Compliance Checklist</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 border-l-8 border-slate-800 hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-slate-800 text-white p-3 rounded mr-4 shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-2xl">01</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">職業安全衛生法 第32條</h3>
                <p class="text-2xl text-slate-600">雇主應對勞工施以從事工作及<span class="bg-yellow-200 px-1 font-bold">預防災變</span>所必要之安全衛生教育、訓練。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 border-l-8 border-slate-600 hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-slate-600 text-white p-3 rounded mr-4 shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-2xl">02</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">職業安全衛生法施行細則 第31條</h3>
                <p class="text-2xl text-slate-600">雇主應執行緊急應變措施，並將其列為職業安全衛生管理計畫之必要項目。</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 border-l-8 border-yellow-500 hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="bg-yellow-500 text-slate-900 p-3 rounded mr-4 shrink-0 shadow-lg">
                <span class="font-bold text-2xl">03</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">職安衛管理辦法 第12-1條 & 12-6條</h3>
                <div class="space-y-2">
                  <p class="text-2xl text-slate-600">第一類事業（顯著風險）應訂定緊急狀況預防、準備及應變計畫。</p>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-2 bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
                    <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="text-red-500 w-6 h-6"></i>
                    <span class="font-bold text-red-600 text-lg">關鍵要求：定期實施演練，且執行紀錄應保存三年。</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PAGE 4: 6 Steps -->
    <section id="section-3" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-5xl w-full">
        <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
          <div class="text-yellow-600 font-bold text-base tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">PAGE 4</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-2">應變計畫規劃六步驟</h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium">SOP 階梯式流程</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-8">
          <!-- Step 1 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="users"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-5 top-14 w-0.5 h-full bg-slate-200 -z-10"></div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">1. 選擇成員</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">跨部門小組（工安、操作、維修、保全），非單人作業。</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 2 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="search"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-5 top-14 w-0.5 h-full bg-slate-200 -z-10"></div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">2. 危害辨識</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">確認具體情境（毒氣洩漏、火災、爆炸、缺氧）。</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 3 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="check-square"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-5 top-14 w-0.5 h-full bg-slate-200 -z-10"></div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">3. 資源評估</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">盤點內部器材（PPE、除汙）與外部支援（消防隊、聯防）。</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 4 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="file-text"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-5 top-14 w-0.5 h-full bg-slate-200 -z-10"></div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">4. 計畫研訂</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">分級動員（一~三級）、區域管制（熱/暖/冷區）。</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 5 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="hard-hat"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute left-5 top-14 w-0.5 h-full bg-slate-200 -z-10"></div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">5. 訓練演練</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">從單元操作（穿戴SCBA）到綜合實兵演練。</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Step 6 -->
          <div class="relative pl-12 py-4 group hover:bg-slate-50 rounded-lg transition-colors cursor-default">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-4 w-10 h-10 bg-slate-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:bg-yellow-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors border-2 border-slate-200">
              <i data-lucide="activity"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">6. 檢討修正</h3>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">AAR (After Action Review)，演練後或製程變更時修訂。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PAGE 5 (NEW): Respiratory Protection EPR -->
    <section id="section-4" class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 bg-slate-100">
      <div class="max-w-5xl w-full">
        <div class="mb-6 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-4">
          <div class="text-yellow-600 font-bold text-base tracking-widest uppercase mb-1">PAGE 5</div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-800 mb-2">呼吸防護 RPE</h2>
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-slate-600 font-medium">從風險評估到防護具選擇</h3>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-8">
          
          <!-- Column 1: Risk Assessment Flow -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 border-b pb-4">
              <i data-lucide="microscope" class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600"></i>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">風險評估流程</h3>
            </div>
            
            <div class="space-y-6 relative">
              <!-- Steps -->
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">1</div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-100">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800">危害確認</h4>
                  <p class="text-base text-slate-500">Hazard Identification</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">2</div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-100">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800">危害特徵描述</h4>
                  <p class="text-base text-slate-500">Hazard Characterization</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">3</div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-100">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800">暴露評估</h4>
                  <p class="text-base text-slate-500">Exposure Assessment</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-4 relative z-10">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xl">4</div>
                <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-slate-100">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800">風險特徵描述</h4>
                  <p class="text-base text-slate-500">Risk Characterization</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Connecting Line -->
              <div class="absolute left-5 top-5 w-0.5 h-[calc(100%-40px)] bg-blue-200 -z-0"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-100 text-center">
              <i data-lucide="arrow-down" class="w-8 h-8 text-slate-400 mx-auto mb-3"></i>
              <div class="bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg font-bold shadow-md inline-block w-full text-xl">
                緊急應變計畫 (ERP)
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Column 2: Selection Logic -->
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 border-b pb-4">
              <i data-lucide="shield" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600"></i>
              <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">防護具選擇決策</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center gap-8">
              
              <!-- High Risk -->
              <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-r-lg">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-2">
                  <h4 class="font-bold text-red-700 text-2xl">IDLH 或 未知危害</h4>
                  <span class="bg-red-200 text-red-800 text-base px-3 py-1 rounded font-bold">高風險</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base text-slate-600 text-xl">立即危害生命健康，或現場狀況不明。</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded border border-red-100 shadow-sm">
                  <div class="bg-red-100 p-3 rounded text-red-600">
                    <i data-lucide="wind" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-2xl text-slate-800">SCBA (供氣式)</span>
                    <p class="text-base text-slate-500 text-xl">自攜式呼吸防護具</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

