            <p class="text-base text-slate-600">LOTO (Lockout/Tagout) 未落實。瓦斯總開關未確實關閉、上鎖或進行氣體偵測。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl p-6 md:p-8 border-t-4 border-slate-700 hover:scale-[1.01] transition-transform">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3">3. 介面整合不足</h4>
            <p class="text-base text-slate-600">施工單位與百貨業主的應變計畫未對接。未考慮顧客疏散動線與施工區的區隔。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
